{"tid":1801012,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"冇人講？今晚11:45PM J2有聖鬥士星矢 聖鬥少女翔，老鬼表示回憶返晒黎","createTime":"2019-12-28T10:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T17:22:01.000Z","uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29a0913ef372017cdfaa7a7465ae33aa70c7fee7","tid":1801012,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:27:51.000Z","msg":"同接近30年前，聖鬥士星矢既時段幾乎一樣，有冇老鬼唸著睇下，係要即場睇，唔係上網重溫，重拾當年挨夜+老豆隨時轉台睇馬+老母隨時趕上床訓，都要冒險睇聖鬥士星矢既滋味？<br />\n<br />\n好記得當年，已經提心吊膽咁唔訓等睇，仲要例遲，明明夠晒鐘做星矢，都係咁做廣告雜誌(宣傳易)，屌佢老母。<br />\n<br />\n而家聖鬥士星矢 聖鬥少女翔陼朝5:30AM仲有第二場，唉如果當年有咁既安排就好。"},{"pid":"ce1b5949d7a3bf10aed8c2c8fcc6eecc5eaa866c","tid":1801012,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n<br />\n但補位有問題...<br />\n<br />\n仲哀過套原創"},{"pid":"5a60228e4dc5cbf12b73f532e93a795d8a7ecf65","tid":1801012,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1b5949d7a3bf10aed8c2c8fcc6eecc5eaa866c","tid":1801012,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n<br />\n但補位有問題...<br />\n<br />\n仲哀過套原創"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"套野係咪好垃圾？"},{"pid":"c51739a8ef236dacf5c1ac4ca9c2ba8b5079dc4c","tid":1801012,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a60228e4dc5cbf12b73f532e93a795d8a7ecf65","tid":1801012,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1b5949d7a3bf10aed8c2c8fcc6eecc5eaa866c","tid":1801012,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n<br />\n但補位有問題...<br />\n<br />\n仲哀過套原創"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"套野係咪好垃圾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"即係你當少女革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3782455b5e1cc4b694487d4e42081865d6a365f","tid":1801012,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB